        <dc:creator><![CDATA[@chri55w chri55w]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
          <p><a href="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/u/chri55w">@chri55w</a> wrote:</p>
          <blockquote>
              <p>in dropitem.java<br>
search for</p>
<p><code>Server.itemHandler.createGroundItem(c, itemId, c.getX(), c.getY(), c.playerItemsN[slot], c.getId());
				c.getItems().deleteItem(itemId, slot, c.playerItemsN[slot]);
				PlayerSave.saveGame(c);
			} else {
				c.sendMessage("This items cannot be dropped.");
			}</code></p>
<p>and replace it with</p>
<p><code>c.sendMessage("The item vanishes as it touches the ground");
				c.getItems().deleteItem(itemId, slot, c.playerItemsN[slot]);
				PlayerSave.saveGame(c);
			} else {
				c.sendMessage("This items cannot be dropped.");
			}</code></p>
          </blockquote>
          <p><a href="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/t/pi-disabling-drops/380076/4">Read full topic</a></p>
